metadata.name: Ephemeral Bliss
metadata.description:
1 of 1 edition
Graphite Pencil on paper mix Digital painting.

"Ephemeral Bliss"

Bliss and misery are all the oppugnant words scoffing the individuals. It has a temporary existence in your mind, not permanent. The intricate thoughts of a stubborn mind are involuntary and buoyed.

We are fond of short time happiness. Through the times we are becoming impatient and in that way we are missing huge satisfaction and pleasure.

Tools:
Fabriano Accademia Drawing Paper
Pencil B, HB, 2B, 4B, 6B, 8B & EE black
Mechanical pencil
Mechanical eraser
Hog hair Brush
Tissue paper
Digitized with Photoshop
